# Online Quiz Application API

## Description
This is a RESTful API for a basic online quiz application built with Node.js and Express.js. It allows users to register, log in, create quizzes, take quizzes, and view results.

## Features
- User Authentication (Register/Login)
- MCQ Quiz Management
  - Create quizzes
  - Get all quizzes
  - Get quiz details
  - Take quizzes and view results

## Requirements
- Node.js
- MongoDB

